Smurfs' Village


Do you wanna take a spin in the city of the Smurfs?


Latest version


Smurfs' Village is an online social game along the same lines as CityVille or FarmVille, in which you have to build your own village of smurfs, manage all its aspects, and play with them to keep them happy.


Inside the game you will meet the most famous smurfs, like Papa Smurf, Smurfette, Lazy, Handy, and Funny smurf. Also, you can participate in fun mini games with any of them, which will give you many benefits for your village, and it will grow each time more and more.


To buy almost all of the game elements you will need to have blueberries, that you can collect little by little, or buy with cash. This way will help keep things moving, but it is not necessary to properly enjoy the game experience.


Smurfs' Village is a social game that is very popular for its own merits. Its characters have a lot of charisma, the graphics are very nice, and the game is fun if you like this genre. So now that you know, start to smurf!


